# CLI Module

{{ project_name }} includes a powerful command-line interface built with [Typer](https://typer.tiangolo.com/).

## Installation

The CLI is automatically available after installing the project:

```bash
uv sync
```

## Usage

```bash
# Show help
uv run {{ package_name }} --help

# Show version
uv run {{ package_name }} --version
```

## Available Commands

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `--help` | Show help message and exit |
| `--version` | Show version and exit |

## Configuration

The CLI respects environment variables defined in `.env`:

```bash
# .env
LOG_LEVEL=debug
```

## Examples

```bash
# Run with verbose output
uv run {{ package_name }} --verbose

# Run in quiet mode
uv run {{ package_name }} --quiet
```

